description: Kailua's' coolest source of sweet and savory goodness is rolling up to you today, so get ready to enjoy A Whale of a Crepe!More than just thin pancakes, crepes are an amazing eating experience all their own. Made fresh from organic ingredients, each and every bite you experience is sure to be something special.Whether you want a taste of pepperoni, an assortment of fine fruit, or something made custom for you, A Whale of a Crepe has it for you!
name: A Whale of a Crepe
